<div class="text-center">
  <span class="eyebrow">Access</span>
  <h2 class="mt-5 text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
    Free Core for everyone. Pro for acceleration.
  </h2>
  <p class="mt-4 text-lg copy-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    Your level decides your path, not whether you can participate. Everyone can
    begin in Free Core; Pro is optional if you want added guidance, curated
    lab options, and faster progress.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-10 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-left">
    <div class="surface-card p-7">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-[var(--color-accent)] font-semibold">Free Core</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-display text-[var(--color-accent)] font-bold">$0</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-xs copy-subtle">Available to all three paths</p>
      <div class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-sm copy-muted">
        <p>✓ Single structured core flow (all levels)</p>
        <p>✓ Core lab set and foundational project work</p>
        <p>✓ Team-readiness fundamentals (Git, PRs, workflow)</p>
        <p>✓ Self-serve progression</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="surface-card p-7 border-[var(--color-accent)]/45">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-[var(--color-accent)] font-semibold">Pro Guided* (Optional)</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-display text-[var(--color-accent)] font-bold">Paid</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-xs copy-subtle">For any path that wants speed, accountability, and deeper guidance</p>
      <div class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-sm copy-muted">
        <p>✓ Guided plan based on your selected path and goals</p>
        <p>✓ Expanded lab library and curated elective tracks</p>
        <p>✓ Deeper feedback on labs and PR-style work</p>
        <p>✓ Faster unblock help in premium Slack channels</p>
        <p>✓ Group Q&A and coaching sessions</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="mt-6 text-sm copy-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    People pay for added guidance and speed, not because fundamentals are locked.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-2 text-xs copy-subtle">*Pro pricing and packaging subject to change. Slack support covers DEVS labs and questions only (not outside course tutoring).</p>

  <div class="mt-8">
    <a href="#notify" class="btn-primary cta-glow inline-flex">
      Join early access <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
